<chapter line="1">Saṅgāmadvayavaṇṇanā</chapter>
<paragraph line="2" number="365"><bold>Ṭhānanisajjavattādinissitā</bold>ti <pageBreak edition="M" number="3.0488" /> ‘‘evaṃ ṭhātabbaṃ, evaṃ nisīditabba’’nti evamādikā. <bold>Saññājananattha</bold>nti cuditakacodakānaṃ saññuppādanatthaṃ. <bold>Anuyogavattaṃ kathāpetvā</bold>ti ‘‘kiṃ anuyogavattaṃ jānāsī’’ti pucchitvā teneva kathāpetvā.</paragraph>
<paragraph line="3" number="375"><bold>Nīlādivaṇṇāvaṇṇavasenā</bold>ti nīlādivaṇṇavasena ārogyatthādiavaṇṇavasena ca.</paragraph>
